{"tid":1259960,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《警告》警察扮示威者唔係咁簡單","createTime":"2019-06-26T17:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T17:42:59.000Z","uid":232126,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b427f150a2c77ded8dca2d8d3035992e8d394c05","tid":1259960,"uid":232126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:21:01.000Z","msg":"依家和理非式抗爭當道<br />\n個個示威者都提哂水唔好衝警局<br />\n但點解警察仲犯低級錯誤比位人入?<br />\n個警察柒咗仲好淡定咁比記者影相<br />\n個樣仲要無任何偽裝<br />\n比人逼埋牆角根本可以叫救護車脫險<br />\n但仲當著咁多人面前捐返入警局<br />\n話比全世界人聽: 我係扮示威者嘅警察! <br />\n根本同雨傘個次一模一樣<br />\n林鄭想將民怨轉移落警察身上<br />\n趁時機成熟就脫身<br />\n所以我好肯定今次件事係故意穿煲"},{"pid":"75bc3a3f11f99d256a71947a6bd7acfdea876e0e","tid":1259960,"uid":232126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bad036f737a74a6d482d880ae3a8157e54fe23","tid":1259960,"uid":232126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63235c7f32350e81a4f233301fe4e2ef94588c45","tid":1259960,"uid":232126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4af10edec12ed8378a5971485a60df3e5101d8","tid":1259960,"uid":18473,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"屌 柒左就柒左啦 佢地就係咁撚簡單啊"},{"pid":"9404a13ada42e2b754e359373373df712edfeddc","tid":1259960,"uid":232126,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1f4af10edec12ed8378a5971485a60df3e5101d8","tid":1259960,"uid":18473,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"屌 柒左就柒左啦 佢地就係咁撚簡單啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:31:16.000Z","msg":"咁簡單就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c205011bcff82ea0cfb0c8d0177ff6d8936eff3c",